  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/541a93f94dff57b7692efbe75661615b.avif?t=1774116712\" width=780 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a quirky road trip as a <strong>tourist in a two-seater peda</strong>l car! Traverse diverse landscapes where you’ll find yourself taking all the wrong paths. Explore your surroundings and take photos along the path<strong>.</strong> <strong>Solo or as a pair</strong>, will you reach the journey's end... or will you roll back down a hill, questioning the very meaning of life?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/f591094b7874f72269a6dd7da6a17ab4.poster.avif?t=1774116712\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/f591094b7874f72269a6dd7da6a17ab4.webm?t=1774116712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/f591094b7874f72269a6dd7da6a17ab4.mp4?t=1774116712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/62bb062cb3b81c9eef5568625fd0bbe4.avif?t=1774116712\" width=780 height=110 /></span><strong>Communication is key!</strong> Each player can only pull the steering lever on their side. <br><strong>Stronger together.</strong> Pedaling and braking is more effective when both pilots are coordinated.  <br><strong>When things get frantic, don't panic.</strong> Trying to pull the handbrake or reverse at the same time can lead to disaster! <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/75b02c4328293a9f10803c9838b34d31.poster.avif?t=1774116712\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/75b02c4328293a9f10803c9838b34d31.webm?t=1774116712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/75b02c4328293a9f10803c9838b34d31.mp4?t=1774116712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/775935248ee5e0483cf300dd530e4a9f.avif?t=1774116712\" width=780 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You steer left, I steer right</strong>, what could possibly go wrong? Everything. From mistimed turns to frantic braking, the road to the finish line is paved with hysterical arguments and near-misses. When you are not in sync and your sense of direction fails, your peaceful seaside stroll quickly turns into complete disaster.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/12edd412e772592bd472dc480809c5a6.poster.avif?t=1774116712\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/12edd412e772592bd472dc480809c5a6.webm?t=1774116712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/12edd412e772592bd472dc480809c5a6.mp4?t=1774116712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/e219187db262fba05926ebe2de8fd820.avif?t=1774116712\" width=780 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While this journey is designed for two, <strong>you can absolutely take on the road alone</strong>. In solo mode, you’ll have full control of the steering and be the only captain on board... but that also means you’ve only got yourself to blame when things go sideways!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/a5009ac9e596bfe93994c2fa1194ac75.poster.avif?t=1774116712\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/a5009ac9e596bfe93994c2fa1194ac75.webm?t=1774116712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/a5009ac9e596bfe93994c2fa1194ac75.mp4?t=1774116712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/c5beef6fa621c222fff9be26708a7ae8.avif?t=1774116712\" width=780 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can't reach the finish line? Don't worry about it. Stop the quadricycle, take a deep breath, and <strong>admire the landscape</strong>. The journey might be a catastrophe, but at least the postcard will look great.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/d5fadbc933c9f691b4452e385b9aa07e.poster.avif?t=1774116712\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/d5fadbc933c9f691b4452e385b9aa07e.webm?t=1774116712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4268470/extras/d5fadbc933c9f691b4452e385b9aa07e.mp4?t=1774116712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
