      "review_text": "Had the fun of my life screaming at my bf to turn. animations 10/10 gameplay 10/10 . honestly loved it and will play it again . would love to have a cam to take photos anywhere also selfies and maybe some intercations with the partner like special emotes ♥ ♥",
