      "votes_up": 0,
      "playtime_at_review": 50,
      "review_text": "Very early in this game, but feels great.  A great coop game that at the moment only supports online coop. Though a simple idea, it can be quite complicated to work together, with person on the left only being able to turn left and person the right only turn right. If both try to turn you carry on straight. \n\nWell work a play if you love coop games with a friend or partner. Be prepared for some disagreements resulting in a lot of laughs. \n\nManaged to play on both steam deck and PC.",
      "timestamp_created": 1774128493
    }
